&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s Degree&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of four (4) years’ relevant experience in Federal contracting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Documented experience of pre- and post-award acquisitions processes with minimal assistance or training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent writing skills and ability to effectively communicate orally and in writing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiar with FAR and VAAR based procurements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
